{
  "video_id": "tNla9nyRMmQ",
  "title": "The real reason American health care is so expensive",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 3380.0,
      "text": "I cannot tell you how obsessed I am with this chart."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 3380.0,
      "end_time": 6000.0,
      "text": "It shows exactly what is wrong with America's"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 6000.0,
      "end_time": 7600.0,
      "text": "conversation about health care."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 7600.0,
      "end_time": 10080.0,
      "text": "On one level, you've seen this chart before."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 10080.0,
      "end_time": 12240.0,
      "text": "It shows health care spending as a share"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 12240.0,
      "end_time": 14460.0,
      "text": "of the economy of a bunch of countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 14460.0,
      "end_time": 17740.0,
      "text": "There's Germany and France and Japan and Canada"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 17740.0,
      "end_time": 19560.0,
      "text": "and oh! There's America."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 19560.0,
      "end_time": 21000.0,
      "text": "But now I want to add something you haven't"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 21000.0,
      "end_time": 22120.0,
      "text": "seen to this chart."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 22120.0,
      "end_time": 24080.0,
      "text": "This is how much of that spending in each country"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 24080.0,
      "end_time": 27160.0,
      "text": "is private and how much is public."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 27160.0,
      "end_time": 28480.0,
      "text": "Here's what's amazing:"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 28480.0,
      "end_time": 30580.0,
      "text": "America's government spending on health care"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 30580.0,
      "end_time": 33140.0,
      "text": "on programs like Medicaid and Medicare and the VA -"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 33140.0,
      "end_time": 35080.0,
      "text": "our versions of socialized medicine."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 35080.0,
      "end_time": 37300.0,
      "text": "It's about the same size as these other countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 37300.0,
      "end_time": 38900.0,
      "text": "These countries where the government runs"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 38900.0,
      "end_time": 40500.0,
      "text": "the whole health care system!"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 40500.0,
      "end_time": 41940.0,
      "text": "And then there's our private spending."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 41940.0,
      "end_time": 44080.0,
      "text": "It's the private insurance system that makes"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 44080.0,
      "end_time": 46180.0,
      "text": "health care in America so expensive."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 46180.0,
      "end_time": 48280.0,
      "text": "Conventional wisdom says that the government is"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 48280.0,
      "end_time": 49980.0,
      "text": "more expensive than the private sector."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 49980.0,
      "end_time": 54080.0,
      "text": "\"It can't say no. It's corrupt, it's inefficient, it's slow.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 54080.0,
      "end_time": 55300.0,
      "text": "\"If you want something done right"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 55300.0,
      "end_time": 56440.0,
      "text": "you give it to the private sector.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 56440.0,
      "end_time": 58520.0,
      "text": "That is what we hear in America all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 58520.0,
      "end_time": 61520.0,
      "text": "And yet here we are with the biggest\n private sector spending the most."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 68080.0,
      "end_time": 70640.0,
      "text": "If you look at the data on physician visits"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 70640.0,
      "end_time": 73560.0,
      "text": "and hospital discharges, you can get rid of one theory."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 73560.0,
      "end_time": 75560.0,
      "text": "Americans don't consume more health care"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 75560.0,
      "end_time": 77100.0,
      "text": "than people in these other countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 77100.0,
      "end_time": 79160.0,
      "text": "We don't go to the doctor more than the Germans"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 79160.0,
      "end_time": 81260.0,
      "text": "or the Japanese. In fact we go to the doctor less."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 81260.0,
      "end_time": 83300.0,
      "text": "The difference between us and them"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 83300.0,
      "end_time": 85400.0,
      "text": "is that we pay more."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 85400.0,
      "end_time": 87500.0,
      "text": "Every time we go to the doctor for everything"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 87500.0,
      "end_time": 89820.0,
      "text": "from an angioplasty to a hip replacement"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 89820.0,
      "end_time": 91320.0,
      "text": "from a c-section"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 91320.0,
      "end_time": 92600.0,
      "text": "to a pain reliever."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 93220.0,
      "end_time": 95380.0,
      "text": "In America, the price for the same procedure"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 95380.0,
      "end_time": 97980.0,
      "text": "at the same hospital, it varies enormously"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 97980.0,
      "end_time": 99660.0,
      "text": "depending on who is footing the bill."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 99660.0,
      "end_time": 101820.0,
      "text": "The price for someone with public insurance"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 101820.0,
      "end_time": 105220.0,
      "text": "like Medicare or Medicaid is often the lowest price."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 105220.0,
      "end_time": 107100.0,
      "text": "These groups he covers so many people"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 107100.0,
      "end_time": 109880.0,
      "text": "that the government can demand lower\n prices from hospitals and doctors"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 109890.0,
      "end_time": 111760.0,
      "text": "and they get those lower prices."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 111760.0,
      "end_time": 113760.0,
      "text": "If the doctors and hospitals say 'No'"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 113760.0,
      "end_time": 115300.0,
      "text": "they lose a ton of business."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 115300.0,
      "end_time": 117080.0,
      "text": "They lose all those people on Medicare"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 117080.0,
      "end_time": 118860.0,
      "text": "all those people on Medicaid."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 118860.0,
      "end_time": 121420.0,
      "text": "But there are hundreds of private insurance companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 121420.0,
      "end_time": 123280.0,
      "text": "And they each cover far fewer people than"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 123280.0,
      "end_time": 124580.0,
      "text": "a Medicare or a Medicaid."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 124580.0,
      "end_time": 126720.0,
      "text": "And each one has to negotiate prices"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 126720.0,
      "end_time": 129200.0,
      "text": "and hospitals and doctors are on their own."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 129199.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131460.0,
      "text": "And if you're uninsured, you have even less leverage."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 131460.0,
      "end_time": 133580.0,
      "text": "Nobody is negotiating on your behalf."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 133580.0,
      "end_time": 135420.0,
      "text": "So you end up paying the highest price."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 135420.0,
      "end_time": 137680.0,
      "text": "One study found that most hospitals charge uninsured"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 137680.0,
      "end_time": 139360.0,
      "text": "patients four times"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 139360.0,
      "end_time": 141480.0,
      "text": "as much as Medicare patients for an ER visit."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 141480.0,
      "end_time": 143740.0,
      "text": "Other countries, they don't have this problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 143740.0,
      "end_time": 145480.0,
      "text": "Instead of every private insurance company"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 145480.0,
      "end_time": 147190.0,
      "text": "negotiating with every healthcare provider."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 147190.0,
      "end_time": 148880.0,
      "text": "There's just this big list."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 148880.0,
      "end_time": 150680.0,
      "text": "The country, the central government, they go"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 150680.0,
      "end_time": 153620.0,
      "text": "and they say, \"If you want to sell to us, to all"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 153620.0,
      "end_time": 155800.0,
      "text": "of our people, then here's what you can charge"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 155800.0,
      "end_time": 158320.0,
      "text": "for a checkup. Here is what you can charge for an MRI"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 158320.0,
      "end_time": 159700.0,
      "text": "or a prescription for Lipitor."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 159700.0,
      "end_time": 161200.0,
      "text": "And so then whether that bill goes to the"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 161200.0,
      "end_time": 162880.0,
      "text": "heavily regulated private insurance"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 162880.0,
      "end_time": 165068.0,
      "text": "companies in Germany or directly to the government"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 165068.0,
      "end_time": 166140.0,
      "text": "like in the UK."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 166140.0,
      "end_time": 168360.0,
      "text": "Each country is telling the doctor or hospital"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 168360.0,
      "end_time": 171000.0,
      "text": "or drug company how much that bill will be."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 171000.0,
      "end_time": 172780.0,
      "text": "And because the government controls access"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 172780.0,
      "end_time": 175260.0,
      "text": "to all of the customers. It's an offer that hospitals"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 175260.0,
      "end_time": 176880.0,
      "text": "and doctors and pharmaceutical companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 176880.0,
      "end_time": 178380.0,
      "text": "typically can't refuse."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 179160.0,
      "end_time": 181260.0,
      "text": "\"I'm going to make him an offer he can't refuse.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 181260.0,
      "end_time": 183940.0,
      "text": "In America the idea is that you'll be a consumer."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 183940.0,
      "end_time": 186740.0,
      "text": "That you'll do what you do when you go to \nBest Buy and buy a television."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 186740.0,
      "end_time": 188460.0,
      "text": "But that just doesn't work in healthcare."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 188460.0,
      "end_time": 189540.0,
      "text": "It doesn't work in healthcare because"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 189540.0,
      "end_time": 191020.0,
      "text": "you often come and get health care when you're"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 191020.0,
      "end_time": 192160.0,
      "text": "unconscious, in an ambulance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 192160.0,
      "end_time": 193380.0,
      "text": "when you're scared,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 193380.0,
      "end_time": 195560.0,
      "text": "when it's for your spouse or your child"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 195560.0,
      "end_time": 198260.0,
      "text": "It is a time when you have the least bargaining power."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 198260.0,
      "end_time": 201320.0,
      "text": "You are not usually capable of saying, 'No.'"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 201320.0,
      "end_time": 203520.0,
      "text": "You're not knowledgeable enough to do it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 203520.0,
      "end_time": 204500.0,
      "text": "you're not comfortable doing it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 204500.0,
      "end_time": 206180.0,
      "text": "or you're not conscious enough to do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 206180.0,
      "end_time": 208440.0,
      "text": "That's why in other countries the government is a"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 208440.0,
      "end_time": 209940.0,
      "text": "person who can say 'No' for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 209940.0,
      "end_time": 211440.0,
      "text": "You can say, 'No, that's too expensive"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 211450.0,
      "end_time": 212580.0,
      "text": "you're going to have to lower your price'"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 212580.0,
      "end_time": 214260.0,
      "text": "because they do have that power."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 217640.0,
      "end_time": 219920.0,
      "text": "Anchor: A new push for single-payer health care"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 219920.0,
      "end_time": 221160.0,
      "text": "right here in the US."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 221160.0,
      "end_time": 222180.0,
      "text": "Demonstrator: What do we want?"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 222180.0,
      "end_time": 223400.0,
      "text": "Crowd: Single-payer!"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 223400.0,
      "end_time": 223960.0,
      "text": "Demonstrator: When do we want it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 223960.0,
      "end_time": 224700.0,
      "text": "Crowd: Now!"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 224700.0,
      "end_time": 226360.0,
      "text": "Anchor: California and others are saying maybe"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 226360.0,
      "end_time": 227980.0,
      "text": "we should adopt the European model."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 227980.0,
      "end_time": 229980.0,
      "text": "Klein: If we decided to create a single-payer system"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 229980.0,
      "end_time": 232140.0,
      "text": "with one of these huge price lists in the US"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 232140.0,
      "end_time": 233860.0,
      "text": "There would be nothing to stop"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 233860.0,
      "end_time": 236040.0,
      "text": "lobbying from hospitals from doctors from"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 236040.0,
      "end_time": 238420.0,
      "text": "drug companies. And those prices would get influenced."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 238420.0,
      "end_time": 240560.0,
      "text": "So we could end up with a single-payer system"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 240560.0,
      "end_time": 242740.0,
      "text": "that is expensive. Even as expensive as"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 242740.0,
      "end_time": 244140.0,
      "text": "our current system."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 244140.0,
      "end_time": 245920.0,
      "text": "It all depends on how much you negotiate down"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 245920.0,
      "end_time": 248000.0,
      "text": "the prices and now in America"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 248000.0,
      "end_time": 250500.0,
      "text": "these groups have so much power\nbecause they are so rich."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 250500.0,
      "end_time": 253480.0,
      "text": "That it's really hard to get them to bring down the prices."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 253480.0,
      "end_time": 254980.0,
      "text": "This is the irony of American healthcare:"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 254980.0,
      "end_time": 258520.0,
      "text": "It's so expensive that it's become \nhard to make it cheaper."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 258519.99999999997,
      "end_time": 261259.99999999997,
      "text": "All that money they make, that becomes political power."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 261260.0,
      "end_time": 263860.0,
      "text": "And years and years and years of overpaying -"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 263860.0,
      "end_time": 265840.0,
      "text": "those are huge industries now."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 265840.0,
      "end_time": 268540.0,
      "text": "And they have a lot of influence in Congress."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 269200.0,
      "end_time": 270360.0,
      "text": "Under a single-payer system"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 270360.0,
      "end_time": 272700.0,
      "text": "if we did drive prices down, doctors and hospitals"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 272700.0,
      "end_time": 274580.0,
      "text": "they would be paid less than they are right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 274580.0,
      "end_time": 276120.0,
      "text": "That might mean some of them close"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 276120.0,
      "end_time": 278340.0,
      "text": "or some go out of business or some move."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 278340.0,
      "end_time": 280560.0,
      "text": "It would be really painful. One person's waste"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 280560.0,
      "end_time": 283180.0,
      "text": "is another person's essential service or local hospital"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 283180.0,
      "end_time": 285460.0,
      "text": "or their income. But then single-payer"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 285460.0,
      "end_time": 287080.0,
      "text": "it's not an all-or-nothing choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 287380.0,
      "end_time": 289460.0,
      "text": "For instance, there's a really interesting section"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 289460.0,
      "end_time": 291400.0,
      "text": "of Bernie Sanders Medicare-for-all bill."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 291400.0,
      "end_time": 292980.0,
      "text": "Where he lays out this interim plan."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 292980.0,
      "end_time": 294460.0,
      "text": "It's a plan he wants while he's setting up"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 294460.0,
      "end_time": 295900.0,
      "text": "his new single-payer system."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 295900.0,
      "end_time": 298380.0,
      "text": "And in that plan, he expands Medicare"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 298380.0,
      "end_time": 299960.0,
      "text": "to cover vision and dental."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 299960.0,
      "end_time": 301400.0,
      "text": "And he opens it to nearly everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 301400.0,
      "end_time": 303560.0,
      "text": "Not just people 65 and older."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 303560.0,
      "end_time": 305240.0,
      "text": "All kids go on Medicare automatically"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 305240.0,
      "end_time": 306780.0,
      "text": "and most adults can buy in."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 306800.0,
      "end_time": 308720.0,
      "text": "That plan, on its own, it wouldn't get American"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 308720.0,
      "end_time": 311500.0,
      "text": "health care spending far down overnight."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 311500.0,
      "end_time": 313120.0,
      "text": "But it would at least begin to recognize"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 313120.0,
      "end_time": 314480.0,
      "text": "what we already know"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 314480.0,
      "end_time": 316340.0,
      "text": "and what most other countries already do:"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 316340.0,
      "end_time": 318600.0,
      "text": "That health care is one of those things the government"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 318600.0,
      "end_time": 321100.0,
      "text": "can do cheaper and better than the private sector."
    }
  ]
}